overview.en: NeoWorld is a MMO sanbox game based on blockchain technology. It is a 3D virtual world created by global players. NASH, a.k.a NeoWorld Cash, is the only currency supported in NeoWorld.
overview.zh: NeoWorld是一个基于区块链技术的多人联网沙盒游戏，也是一个由全球用户共同协作创建的3D虚拟世界。NASH 的全名为 NeoWorld Cash, 是 NeoWorld 的唯一货币。
